{"type": "article", "id": 37945, "title": "猜猜看，摄影棚能缩到多小？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-02-19T23:04:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 21020, "name": "Feist Forest"}, {"id": 28679, "name": "Joynout"}, {"id": 37787, "name": "Sanwa Supply"}, {"id": 37788, "name": "Brunt"}, {"id": 37789, "name": "Léo Gratier"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 498, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170219215327ehAVwmZUgWQ5DrSN.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Light Room by Sanwa Supply</h3><p>摄影离不开光线，但要把东西拍得更美不一定非得用到那些高价的照明器材，或是苦苦守候自然光的完美时机。由日本公司 <a href=\"http://direct.sanwa.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sanwa Supply</a> 推出的这款 Light Room 便携式摄影盒可以被视作一个迷你版的摄影棚，仅重 190 克。顶部边缘配有一条包含 20 个 LED 小灯的灯带，由 USB 口提供电力，可以提供 300 流明的亮度。它采用了平板式设计，使用完只要经过简单的折叠就能变成一个仅厚 3 厘米的壳子，收纳起来相当方便。这是它的<a href=\"http://direct.sanwa.co.jp/ItemPage/200-DG014\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 3980 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215355QlpPsRGNO5Y172MT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215356WEzjK0hnwyIT9r7u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215356XeBHaG1Sd83vwtIy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215356iJqOunKYNIaWZf7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215356ZeworxsDQWCqXSN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215356ihaLcQR24bDNlkZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Powerstation by Brunt</h3><p>电子产品越来越多，散乱的充电线就成了桌面的美观杀手。来自美国洛杉矶的配件设计公司 <a href=\"https://brunt.co/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Brunt</a> 为此设计了一款多功能的充电座 Powerstation，低调的黑金配色放在哪里都不会显得突兀。它可以用作书架或是电脑支架，正面支持无线充电，其他常见的充电接口和插座则以“眼不见为净”的宗旨藏在了基座两侧和背后。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/965750266/powerstation-multi-function-electric-device-for-de\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 79 美元。如果你的手机不支持无线充电也没有关系，它还附赠 iPhone/Android 用的接收器。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017021921552608qiEk2ZCuAUWYLd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732353\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215527oRS6lIa08UZWfCB9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.389706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215527wBQMhjzPEIqLJbg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215526kQqnExrpu5jXYaKA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.329412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702192155279HhQLiuFVemARGat.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.338235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Loop D Loops glass panels by Feist Forest</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.feistforest.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Feist Forest</a> 是一个英国的手工艺工作室，创始人 Vicki Turner 与彩色玻璃工匠 Flora Jamieson 合作，将以海洋为主题创作的插画系列 <a href=\"http://www.feistforest.com/blog//loop-d-loops-edition-no2\" rel=\"nofollow\">Loop D Loops</a> 制作成了四块精美的彩色玻璃板。所有玻璃都采用人工吹制，并附赠对应的原图卡片，这是它的<a href=\"http://www.feistforest.com/store/loopdloopno2\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 79 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017021921544496rtOis4FgMmqkD8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215443RxiNzguoea2n40ES.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215444okw3BXs1R8ZmTWDd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.380247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215443JypiIM5F01Ro3fa2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215443z63FvQ4GP9hjJ0XH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Daydream by Joynout</h3><p>忙碌了一整天，是不是特别想在躺椅上随性地“瘫”着？最近，设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.joynout.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Joynout</a> 以无限符号为灵感设计了一款名为 Daydream 的躺椅，它由两块配有柔软衬垫的平板交叉而成，形成了一个 V 字型的空间，最多可供两个人休息，被分成多段的平板还能根据需要改变角度。这款躺椅将在今年的米兰设计周上展出，Joynout 为平板设计了十种颜色，可以组合出不同的风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215503oLmwQY8ey3HzUsr1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.631250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215503lS54xYeGbmBhTyqN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215504lQJOkM42acjdrFDq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.911111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215503BQmHvTdiy2JshMA8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215505bnHLYAuBpZa9Kxvf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.822222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215505h6KHYjfBNaT3OtQX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>TV Series Posters by Léo Gratier</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/leogratier/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Léo Gratier</a> 是一位来自法国的设计师，他为几部知名的电视连续剧创作了极简风的海报。Gratier 并没有尝试描绘太多细节，而是通过留白和粉蓝的组合制作具有高识别度的人物剪影。如果你喜欢他的风格，还可以关注由他设计的独立服饰品牌 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UnDoubleA/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alpha’art</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215624EUaobhqzlPkWAT4C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215624mNUyEafRT2Gexk4B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215624z93nXFJ7Yl0t5GuH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215626BqiAgZ4QO65yFENb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702192156265xNBU0KMZkfmAawY.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664444\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702192156261sFS4lz2fenuMO6h.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.747778\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Seasonal Chocolate by Jarosław Morawski</h3><p>Seasonal Chocolate 是波兰平面设计系学生 <a href=\"http://www.jaroslawmorawski.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jarosław Morawski</a> 以季节变化为主题设计的一款<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/46481519/Seasonal-Chocolate\" rel=\"nofollow\">概念包装</a>。Morawski 不仅为春夏秋冬设计了色调温和且风格简洁的插画，还构思了对应的巧克力风味。当四个包装组合到一起，又形成了一幅完整的风景画，看起来非常令人惬意。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215419b6WqBMmrEUXu03y1.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.883139\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215419INmOuQACvxW1YES3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.154553\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170219215420nBOC2SumJPl0r6Tb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.072574\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}